          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1662449913738-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1662449913738-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the linguine is cooking, wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>When the linguine is almost done, add the <strong>spinach</strong> to the pot<strong> </strong>and cook for 30 secs or until the spinach has wilted, then drain the <strong>linguine & spinach</strong> and reserve a cup of <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1662449916969-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
